tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE biometric_payment_data (
    user_id INT,
    biometric_data VARCHAR(255),
    payment_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    transaction_date DATE,
    machine_learning_prediction VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE machine_learning_models (
    model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name TEXT,
    algorithm_type TEXT,
    features JSONB,
    accuracy FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE predictive_analytics (
    prediction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    model_id INT,
    prediction_result JSONB,
    prediction_time TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE Biometric_Data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  biometric_type VARCHAR(50),
  biometric_data VARCHAR(255),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Payment_Data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  payment_amount DECIMAL(10,2),
  payment_date DATE,
  payment_method VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Machine_Learning_Models (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_name VARCHAR(100),
  model_type VARCHAR(50),
  training_data_table VARCHAR(100),
  accuracy DECIMAL(5,2)
);

CREATE TABLE Predictive_Analytics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  prediction_id INT,
  user_id INT,
  predicted_value DECIMAL(10,2),
  prediction_date DATE
);
